  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6311573/" class="title-link">不懂乱改的地方太多了，解释也太简单了</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6311573"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/65091134/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u65091134-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/65091134/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">上有黄庭</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-10-03"
      class="main-meta">2013-10-03 19:00:02</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6311573_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  没有版本上的依据还乱改，而且还改错了，比如46页的“叹与俗相返之远也”，本来人家写返是对的，非要改成反…… 而且释太少太简单了，难解之处，几乎处处没有解释，反而是简单易懂之处倒都有解释，是书水平不高

