  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2020828">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2020828/" class="title-link">一版一印</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2020828"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2536717/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2536717-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2536717/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">飞骢</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-05-11"
      class="main-meta">2009-05-11 20:00:02</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2020828_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                     《道德经》真正是辞微旨远，五千言，字字饱满，句句圆润，掷地不仅有声，还要弹起蹦跳几下。老子随手一挥，气吞万里，席卷宇宙，包藏万物。     王弼之注与原经文浑然一体，有如夫唱妇随之感，一唱一和而使境界臻于圆满。不可不谓王弼之深得老子意趣也。 

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2020828/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">4有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
