  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4670090/" class="title-link">《老子》之道——从比喻说起</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4670090"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/metaphorqian/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u28180038-36.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/metaphorqian/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">安漫漫</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-02-23"
      class="main-meta">2011-02-23 11:36:47</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4670090_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                        老子写《道德经》，区区五千言，却生动详尽地阐述了在他心目中无法阐透的“道”，其中最大的帮手莫过于运用比喻的手法，其于形于本于质于神多方面描摹了“道”这个无法触摸无法言传的对象。我向来“好事”，倒愿意借此机会找出王弼校注本《道德经》中有关“道”的比喻，...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4670090/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
